ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in finding and communicating with the publisher.

ivardefs.name: copyright
ivardefs.desc: A copyright statement relating to the structure map and/or its contents. Copyright statements are generally legal restrictions on the use and publishing of the structure map.

ivardefs.name: date
ivardefs.desc: The date  (and optionally time) when the structure map was published. The date must change when the business version changes and it must change if the status code changes. In addition, it should change when the substantive content of the structure map cha

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A free text natural language description of the structure map from a consumer's perspective.

ivardefs.name: experimental
ivardefs.desc: A Boolean value to indicate that this structure map is authored for testing purposes (or education/evaluation/marketing) and is not intended to be used for genuine usage.

ivardefs.name: group_
ivardefs.desc: Organizes the mapping into manageable chunks for human review/ease of maintenance.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: A formal identifier that is used to identify this structure map when it is represented in other formats, or referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance.

ivardefs.name: import_
ivardefs.desc: Other maps used by this map (canonical URLs).

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: A legal or geographic region in which the structure map is intended to be used.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A natural language name identifying the structure map. This name should be usable as an identifier for the module by machine processing applications such as code generation.

ivardefs.name: publisher
ivardefs.desc: The name of the organization or individual that published the structure map.

ivardefs.name: purpose
ivardefs.desc: Explanation of why this structure map is needed and why it has been designed as it has.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of this structure map. Enables tracking the life-cycle of the content.

ivardefs.name: structure_
ivardefs.desc: A structure definition used by this map. The structure definition may describe instances that are converted, or the instances that are produced.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A short, descriptive, user-friendly title for the structure map.

ivardefs.name: url

ivardefs.name: version
